### 🌍 Base API URL and Test Post ID
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001
@id = 1  
# Replace with actual post ID if needed

### 🛒 Get All Posts (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts

###

### 🔍 Get Post by ID (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{id}}

###

### ➕ Create a New Post (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "하하하하하",
  "userId": "1"
}

###

### ✏ Update Post Information (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "Updated Post",
  "password": 2000
}

###

### 🗑 Delete a Post (DELETE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{id}}